children.name: User should verify that product added to shopping cart successFully
Given I am on home page
When I click on currency dropdown
And I click on £pound Sterling
And I click on Desktops tab
And I call selectMenu and pass all desktop "Show AllDesktops"
And I click on sort by position A to Z "Name (A - Z)"
And I select the product "HTC Touch HD"
And I get the text product "HTC Touch HD"
And I enter qty one using select class
And I click on add to cart button
And I get the message Success: You have added "HTC Touch HD" to your shopping cart!
